
## 🔧 How It Works
1. Users submit a tarot reading request via the form
2. Requests appear in the "درخواست‌های دریافتی" section
3. Admin can reply to each request directly from the page
4. All data is stored in browser's localStorage

## 📝 Admin Instructions
- Scroll to **"درخواست‌های دریافتی"** section
- Each un-replied request has a textarea and "ارسال پاسخ" button
- Type your reply and click the button
- Reply will be saved and displayed immediately

## 🛠️ Customization
- Change `background` in `.tarot-bg` for different tarot cards
- Modify colors in `style.css` (search for `#daa520` - gold theme)
- Add blog posts in `#blog` section of `index.html`

## 🔒 Privacy Note
All data is stored locally in your browser's localStorage.
To make it server-persistent, connect a backend API.

## 📦 Deploy to GitHub
1. Create a GitHub repository
2. Upload all files
3. Go to Settings > Pages
4. Select "main" branch as source
5. Your site will be live at: `https://[username].github.io/[repo-name]`

